hat maximize long-term gain while minimizing oscillation. The entire pipeline forms a temporally aware, self-diagnosing active learning loop that evolves both data acquisition and model optimization in tandem. By predicting uncertainty before it manifests and reusing past refinement knowledge, ProActivePanoptic achieves higher accuracy with fewer labeled pixels, especially in long-tail scenarios involving rare object configurations. We expect to surpass PanoRefineAL by 3–4% mIoU under 25% labeling budgets on Cityscapes and BDD10K, and demonstrate zero-shot generalization to unseen domains like ACDC (adverse weather) via prototype transfer.",
